the bottomonium-nuclear matter and charmonium-nuclear matter\ninteraction strengths. Are also studied the $\\Upsilon$ and $\\eta_b$ mass shifts\nin a heavy quark (heavy meson) symmetry limit. In addition, an initial study\nwas done to investigate the influence of the choice of the form factor on our\npredictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 Jan 2022 01:44:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-25"}
