he original multiple proofs. Lastly, our experimental results\ndemonstrate that our QMPs-based zk-SNARK performs nearly 13.9$\\times$faster\nthan the existing QAPs-based zk-SNARK in proving time, and 17.6$\\times$faster\nin Setup time, for high-dimension matrix multiplication.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 Jan 2022 05:33:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2022 02:57:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 28 May 2023 07:02:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-30"}
